"""
be_shadow_manager.py  v4.0.0
BotA Read-Only Shadow Trade Manager

PURPOSE
  Runs two shadow policy lanes alongside the unchanged production static closer.
  Writes only to `shadow_log`. Never touches `signals`.

  STATIC_MIRROR  — mirrors live TP-first static closer via OANDA replay (canary)
  BE_1.0R        — arms break-even once +1.0R MFE is reached in the shadow

CHANGES FROM v3
  [1] First-run anchor bug fixed.
      `last_polled_at` is NEVER used as a candle replay anchor.
      When `last_candle_ts_processed` is null, fetch_from = signal `created_at`.
      Applies to both `process_active_signal` and `reconcile_orphaned_shadow_rows`.
      The `elif last_polled_at` fallback branches are removed entirely.

  [2] Reconciliation retry/cooldown added.
      Unresolved reconciliation rows (Cases A/B/C) are no longer retried every cycle.
      Cooldown enforced via `last_polled_at` check against RECONCILE_RETRY_COOLDOWN_MINUTES.
      Max-age check: rows older than RECONCILE_MAX_AGE_HOURS are permanently abandoned
      (shadow_state = CLOSED, shadow_outcome = null, last_error = reconcile_abandoned).
      This eliminates redundant OANDA/Supabase calls on dead cases.

  [3] API efficiency hardened.
      - last_polled_at removed as replay anchor — no more defensive overlaps that cause
        reprocessing of already-evaluated candles
      - Reconciliation skips rows within cooldown window before any API call
      - Max-age check fires before any fetch attempt

REQUIRED ENV KEYS
  SUPABASE_URL                        full project URL https://xxx.supabase.co
  SUPABASE_SERVICE_KEY                service role key (rotate before use)
  OANDA_API_TOKEN                     new token after rotation
  OANDA_MODE                          must be exactly PRACTICE or LIVE — hard fail

OPTIONAL ENV KEYS
  SHADOW_ENABLED                       true | false   (default: false)
  BE_R_THRESHOLD                       float          (default: 1.0)
  MIRROR_DIVERGENCE_THRESHOLD_PIPS     float          (default: 2.0)
  TERMINAL_LOOKBACK_HOURS              int            (default: 96)
  RECONCILE_RETRY_COOLDOWN_MINUTES     int            (default: 60)
  RECONCILE_MAX_AGE_HOURS              int            (default: 96)

ENV FILE LOAD ORDER (first file wins per key)
  .env.runtime → .env → config/strategy.env → strategy.env
"""

